    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "2 Mar 50",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "Telephone call received from Lt Col Nunamaker",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Tennessee Military District 1130, 2 March. He stated that",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "A. There is a radar station near Knoxville which has",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "been in operation about 3 weeks. This radar station is being",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "operated by station WROL of Knoxville.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "[unclear]",
      "status": "needs_image_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "B. On 1 March at 2135 hours the station picked up",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "an object 340 degrees and 18 miles from Knoxville altitude",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "40,000 feet. Direction and distance put the object directly",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "over Oak Ridge. AEC Security Division Chief at Oak Ridge",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "checked with Smyrna Air Base Nashville which reported it had",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "no flight plan for any plane being in that vicinity and",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "altitude.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "C. On 2 March at 1105 station picked up object at",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "335 degrees and 18 miles from Knoxville altitude 40,000",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "feet. AEC Security Div Chief checked with Smyrna Air Base",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "with negative results.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "D. AEC Sec Div Chief is not certain as to operational",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "efficiency of radar unit and requested Smyrna AB to send",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "qualified radar operator. Smyrna has no personnel so",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "qualified. Smyrna commander suggested Third Army send",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "qualified radar operator to check equipment.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "INDEXED - 19",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "RECORDED - 19",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "MAR 23 1950",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "E. Data from radar was limited to:",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "1. Bearing, distance and altitude on each object.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "2. Third Army queried 14th Air Force to determine",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "if 14th AF had training flights over the Knoxville area on",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "1 and 2 March. Answer was no.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
